{"text": "The graphical method for the determination of the instantaneous velocity is always not a convenient method.", "fibs": ["method"]}
{"text": "For this, we must carefully plot the position–time graph and calculate the value of average velocity as ∆t becomes smaller and smaller.", "fibs": ["plot"]}
