{"text": "Then, we calculate ∆x/∆t from the data for decreasing the value of ∆t and find the limiting value as we have done in Table 3.1 or use differential calculus for the given expression and calculate dx/dt at different instants as done in the following example.", "fibs": ["∆x/∆t"]}
