{"text": "Note that the x-t, v-t, and a-t graphs shown in several figures in this chapter have sharp kinks at some points implying that the functions are not differentiable at these points.", "fibs": ["chapter"]}
{"text": "In any realistic situation, the functions will be differentiable at all points and the graphs will be smooth.", "fibs": ["situation"]}
